{"tid":2403314,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，弟弟無辜被告藏毒！弟弟竟然認罪！","createTime":"2021-02-11T04:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:15:06.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"983fd87bcd5995b188dcf977ee1f5b3de10c3b01","tid":2403314,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"我弟弟今年18歲，<br />\n<br />\n他和朋友在唱k的時候，剛好有警察巡查，<br />\n<br />\n誰知他朋友立即把身上的k仔丟在地下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到警察來到的時候，警察問起弟弟，地上那包k是否他的。<br />\n<br />\n年少無知的弟弟，不知后果嚴重，<br />\n<br />\n為了不耽誤明天上班，竟然承認是他的。<br />\n<br />\n然后便被告他藏毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件是發生在7月的，<br />\n<br />\n家里一直不知道，直到8月，監控管上門才知道。<br />\n<br />\n弟弟他昨天上庭，現時被關到壁屋還押所，<br />\n<br />\n現在等各懲教的報告， 到9月18號再上庭判罪，之后正式入獄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我弟弟是無辜的，可惜他蠢到認罪，<br />\n<br />\n我想問，現在補救還來得及嗎？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請問現時能做些甚麼幫助他？<br />\n<br />\n我是他姐姐，父母的態度就由得他坐監，我很生氣！<br />\n<br />\n無緣無故被背上罪名，還留案底，還要關幾個月半年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望有律師給予我意見，<br />\n<br />\n然后看勝算再打官司，<br />\n<br />\n律師我真的不會找，有名的又很貴..<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望有人能幫我，現留下telegram: <br />\n@hugo19911<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我非常需要幫忙！！謝謝！"},{"pid":"2c1cdd91c29be475e45957cda632f5a4a960fea3","tid":2403314,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518e37d53c3821f7a3ea88696141ec8e5073159e","tid":2403314,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0ca31e6aaed7659626e606601993c6520e0ab6","tid":2403314,"uid":38719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0